1) download Nodejs from  https://nodejs.org/en
2) open terminal and run these code in backend
  -    npm install express jsonwebtoken bcyptjs dotenv mongoose cookie-parse cloudinary
3) run this too in frontend
  npm install -D nodemon
  npm i @chakra-ui/react
  npm install @chakra-ui/icons
  npm npm i date-fns

4) get the .env file from me, and move it to the backend folder
5) open 2 terminals and navigate to backend and frontend respectively
    and run `npm run dev` in both of the terminal
6) open http://localhost:3000/ in browser
